    "Name": "Chevalier (Speed)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Chevalier Light Tank (Speed)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>7/11 (Wheeled)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>225 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Chevalier Light Tank, originally produced for the Star League, suffered heavy losses during the Succession Wars as Successor States cannibalized its design for parts. Only Millennium Industries continued production, later acquired by ComStar.\n\nIn use with the 31st Division of the Com Guards, this variant increases the Chevalier's top speed to 119 km/h. In order to accomplish this, it had to remove two tons of armor and one of the missile launchers.",
